<template>
  <el-table :data="list" style="width: 100%;padding-top: 15px;">
    <el-table-column label="Block Name" mid-width="50" align="center">
      <template slot-scope="scope">
        {{ scope.row.blockNumber }}
      </template>
    </el-table-column>

    <el-table-column label="BlockHash" width="400" align="center">
      <template slot-scope="scope">
        {{ scope.row.blockHash }}
      </template>
    </el-table-column>
  </el-table>

</template>

<script>
import { getNewestBlockInfo } from '@/api/block'

export default {
  filters: {
    statusFilter(status) {
      const statusMap = {
        success: 'success',
        pending: 'danger'
      }
      return statusMap[status]
    },
    orderNoFilter(str) {
      return str.substring(0, 30)
    }
  },
  data() {
    return {
      list: null,
      activities: [{
        content: '活动按期开始',
        timestamp: '2018-04-15'
      }, {
        content: '通过审核',
        timestamp: '2018-04-13'
      }, {
        content: '创建成功',
        timestamp: '2018-04-11'
      }]
    }
  },
  created() {
    this.fetchData()
  },
  methods: {
    fetchData() {
      getNewestBlockInfo().then(response => {
        const da = response.data.map(obj => ({ blockNumber: obj.blockNumber, blockHash: obj.blockHash }))
        // console.log(da)
        this.list = da
      })
    }
  }
}
</script>
